00:21:12.890 --> 00:21:16.400 align:middle line:84%
Maybe we're close to one of
these and we are searching.

00:21:16.400 --> 00:21:19.820 align:middle line:84%
We are simulating environments,
searching for ways

00:21:19.820 --> 00:21:23.862 align:middle line:84%
so that we can avoid these
great crises in our lives.

00:21:23.862 --> 00:21:25.820 align:middle line:84%
And when I've said this
to people in the past--

00:21:25.820 --> 00:21:27.560 align:middle line:90%
I've had this conversation--

00:21:27.560 --> 00:21:30.590 align:middle line:84%
I've said it to a large
audience, I've said one on one.

00:21:30.590 --> 00:21:33.950 align:middle line:84%
And when I suggest these
possibilities of actually

00:21:33.950 --> 00:21:37.070 align:middle line:84%
