00:35:09.780 --> 00:35:13.670 align:middle line:84%
The science gives us rock solid
reasons to think differently.

00:35:13.670 --> 00:35:16.440 align:middle line:84%
But the events of
today's world tell us

00:35:16.440 --> 00:35:19.330 align:middle line:90%
