00:35:19.330 --> 00:35:22.380 align:middle line:84%
So, as we begin to embrace the
possibility that we are living

00:35:22.380 --> 00:35:26.490 align:middle line:84%
in a simulated world, we also
unlock the deepest mysteries

00:35:26.490 --> 00:35:27.684 align:middle line:90%
of our existence.

00:35:27.684 --> 00:35:29.100 align:middle line:84%
At the same time
we're discovering

00:35:29.100 --> 00:35:32.010 align:middle line:84%
what it takes for us to become
the best people we can be

00:35:32.010 --> 00:35:34.540 align:middle line:84%
